high_descs: turn around and walk over to the fridge.

take the banana with you to the sink.
Put the banana in the sink.
turn around again and go back to the fridge.
Open the door to the fridge and take out another banana.
take that banana to the sink as well.
Put the banana next to the other banana in the sink.

Put the banana in the sink.

Pick up the banana from the bottom shelf of the fridge.
Turn around to walk back to the sink.
Put the banana in the sink in front of the other banana.

Place the banana next to the sink.
